articles.headline: How every five-star college football recruit fits at his new school
articles.description: There are 21 five-stars in the Class of 2026. We look at how they got to their teams and what they'll do in college.

images.name: Chris Henry Jr. [608x342]
images.caption: Chris Henry Jr. committed to Ohio State in July of 2023.

images.name: Keenyi Pepe [800x800]
images.caption: Keenyi Pepe adds another impressive building block to USC's OL class.

articles.byline: Craig Haubert, Eli Lederman and Tom Luginbill

articles.headline: Jaden O'Neal gives Florida State highest-rated QB since 2022 class
articles.description: Four-star quarterback Jaden O'Neal, ranked No. 112 in the 2026 ESPN 300, announced his commitment to Florida State on Sunday night, sealing a long-anticipated flip for the former Oklahoma pledge.

articles.headline: Defensive end Richard Wesley commits to Texas Longhorns
articles.description: Defensive end Richard Wesley, a 6-foot-5, 250-pound pass rusher from Chatsworth, California, has committed to Texas, the No. 18 overall prospect in the 2026 ESPN 300 announced on Sunday night following an official visit with the Longhorns this weekend.

articles.headline: Ex-Buckeye Kirk Barton facing charge after fatal crash in Ohio
articles.description: Kirk Barton, a former captain at Ohio State who went on to play in the NFL, faces an aggravated vehicular manslaughter charge following a fatal crash early Saturday morning.

articles.headline: Notre Dame lands commitments from Khary Adams, Joey O'Brien
articles.description: Notre Dame landed pledges from a pair of top 2026 defensive back targets Friday, edging a trio of recruiting rivals to the commitments of No. 8 cornerback Khary Adams and No. 4 athlete prospect Joey O'Brien.

articles.headline: Oklahoma fills need with commitment of 4-star QB Bowe Bentley
articles.description: Four-star quarterback Bowe Bentley, No. 261 in the 2026 ESPN 300, announced his commitment to Oklahoma over LSU on Friday.

videos.headline: Howell rallies UNC back with amazing 20-yard TD run
videos.description: After being down by 21 points in the third quarter, Sam Howell gives North Carolina a 52-45 lead over Wake Forest with a 20-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell rallies UNC back with amazing 20-yard TD run) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNC WR fights to turn near-INT into amazing one-handed catch
videos.description: Sam Howell lets it fly and is nearly picked off by Ja'Sir Taylor, but Dyami Brown rips the ball away with one arm and comes down with a 55-yard catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNC WR fights to turn near-INT into amazing one-handed catch) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Newsome breaks off 75-yard TD for UNC
videos.description: Sam Howell throws a pass to Dazz Newsome, who races to the end zone for a 75-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Newsome breaks off 75-yard TD for UNC) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morin's amazing catch helps set up a TD for Wake
videos.description: Taylor Morin wins the fight with a defender to come down with a great 28-yard catch.  A few plays later, Sam Hartman hangs on to the high snap and runs it in.  He's hit and fumbles, but is able to recover the ball for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Morin's amazing catch helps set up a TD for Wake) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taylor rips ball away from Brown for hard-fought INT
videos.description: Dyami Brown appears to make a catch on a deep ball, but Ja'Sir Taylor fights hard and takes the ball away for an interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor rips ball away from Brown for hard-fought INT) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hartman increases Wake Forest's lead with TD pass to Greene
videos.description: Sam Hartman and Donavon Greene connect on a scoring strike for the second time in the game as Green's 18-yard TD increases the lead over North Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hartman increases Wake Forest's lead with TD pass to Greene) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howell cuts into Wake Forest's lead with 46-yard TD strike to Carter
videos.description: Sam Howell throws throws his fifth touchdown pass of the game as he connects with Michael Carter on a 46-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell cuts into Wake Forest's lead with 46-yard TD strike to Carter) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howell's sixth TD pass ties UNC with Wake Forest
videos.description: Sam Howell throws a 10-yard touchdown pass to Garrett Walston, tying North Carolina's game with Wake Forest at 45-45.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell's sixth TD pass ties UNC with Wake Forest) 2020/11/14 ESHEET
